The crypto industry has long faced challenges in onboarding new users due to the complexity of converting fiat to crypto. Coinbase Onramp addresses this by providing a developer-friendly, secure, and scalable solution that simplifies the process. By integrating with Base, Coinbase’s Ethereum Layer 2 solution, Onramp ensures low-cost transactions, making it ideal for applications ranging from DeFi to personal finance and AI-driven payments.

Moreover, Onramp’s zero-fee USDC transactions and built-in compliance features make it a cost-effective and regulatory-compliant choice for developers. Its headless API empowers developers to create tailored experiences, ensuring that users remain within the app ecosystem, which boosts engagement and retention.

